I deeply regret the reckless manner in which I drove while rushing to the airport to pick up my family members. My sense of urgency led me to operate the vehicle aggressively, surpassing the prescribed speed limit. Additionally, I made a poor decision to respond to a text message from my cousin while driving, which ultimately resulted in a collision with a guardrail. Thankfully, no other individuals were harmed as a result of this incident.

